<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak 8 mushrooms 5m then drain]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
reduce the duck stock with soaked mushrooms (1), 1 tbsp rice wine, 2 tbsp soy sauce, 0.5 tsp salt, 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
mix marinade ingredients, glaze over duck, stand on rack over greaseproof paper 15m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
roast duck at 200C for 8 - 12 mins (depending on whether breast / thigh) then rest 5m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
cook noodels 2.5m, drain, rinse in hot water, drain again, then place in individual bowls]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
fish out mushrooms from soup, and place with noodles, coriander leaves, chopped spring onions, thinkly sliced duck]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
sive the stock over the bowls and serve
]]></step>
</directions>
